!   Test

!   Gets the temperature

    script Temperature

    variable URL
    variable Result
    variable MAC
    variable IPAddr

    put `192.168.1.166` into IPAddr
    put `f09e9ead8f39` into MAC

Loop:
    gosub to GetTemperature
    wait 5
    go to Loop

    exit

GetTemperature:
    put `http://` cat IPAddr cat `/?mac=` cat MAC cat `&msg=temp` into URL
    get Result from URL
    or begin
       print MAC
       return
    end
    print MAC cat ` ` cat Result
    return
